{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":984,"text":"Tell your daughters of this year,"},{"time":3280,"text":"how we woke needing coffee"},{"time":5400,"text":"but discovered instead cadavers\nstrewn about our morning papers,"},{"time":9240,"text":"waterlogged facsimiles\nof our sisters, spouses, small children."},{"time":14600,"text":"Say to your baby of this year\nwhen she asks, as she certainly should,"},{"time":18240,"text":"tell her it was too late coming."},{"time":19840,"text":"Admit even in the year we leased freedom,\nwe didn't own it outright."},{"time":24320,"text":"There were still laws\nfor every way we used our privates"},{"time":27160,"text":"while they pawed at the soft folds of us,"},{"time":29680,"text":"grabbed with no concern for consent,"},{"time":32439,"text":"no laws made for the men\nthat enforced them."},{"time":35080,"text":"We were trained to dodge,"},{"time":37520,"text":"to wait, to cower and cover,"},{"time":40160,"text":"to wait more, still, wait."},{"time":43080,"text":"We were told to be silent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45440,"text":"But speak to your girls of this wartime,"},{"time":47720,"text":"a year preceded by a score of the same,"},{"time":50320,"text":"so as in two decades before,"},{"time":52600,"text":"we wiped our eyes,"},{"time":54160,"text":"laced caskets with flags,"},{"time":56080,"text":"evacuated the crime scene of the club,"},{"time":58280,"text":"caterwauled in the street,"},{"time":59600,"text":"laid our bodies on the concrete\nagainst the outlines of our fallen,"},{"time":62920,"text":"cried, \"Of course we mattered,\""},{"time":64879,"text":"chanted for our disappeared."},{"time":66280,"text":"The women wept this year."},{"time":68440,"text":"They did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69680,"text":"In the same year, we were ready."},{"time":72160,"text":"The year we lost our inhibition\nand moved with courageous abandon"},{"time":75280,"text":"was also the year we stared down barrels,"},{"time":77800,"text":"sang of cranes in skies,\nducked and parried,"},{"time":80160,"text":"caught gold in hijab,\ncollected death threats,"},{"time":82640,"text":"knew ourselves as patriots,"},{"time":84000,"text":"said, \"We're 35 now, time we settled down\nand found a running mate,\""},{"time":87240,"text":"made road maps for infant joy,\nshamed nothing but fear,"},{"time":90400,"text":"called ourselves fat and meant, of course,"},{"time":92680,"text":"impeccable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93920,"text":"This year, we were women,"},{"time":95880,"text":"not brides or trinkets,"},{"time":97680,"text":"not an off-brand gender,"},{"time":99200,"text":"not a concession, but women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101360,"text":"Instruct your babies."},{"time":102680,"text":"Remind them that the year has passed\nto be docile or small."},{"time":106080,"text":"Some of us said for the first time\nthat we were women,"},{"time":108720,"text":"took this oath of solidarity seriously."},{"time":111120,"text":"Some of us bore children\nand some of us did not,"},{"time":113400,"text":"and none of us questioned\nwhether that made us real"},{"time":115840,"text":"or appropriate or true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117640,"text":"When she asks you of this year,"},{"time":119800,"text":"your daughter, whether your offspring\nor heir to your triumph,"},{"time":122729,"text":"from her comforted side of history\nteetering towards woman,"},{"time":125760,"text":"she will wonder and ask voraciously,"},{"time":128080,"text":"though she cannot fathom your sacrifice,"},{"time":130039,"text":"she will hold your estimation of it holy,"},{"time":132840,"text":"curiously probing, \"Where were you?"},{"time":135360,"text":"Did you fight?\nWere you fearful or fearsome?"},{"time":138400,"text":"What colored the walls of your regret?"},{"time":140280,"text":"What did you do for women\nin the year it was time?"},{"time":142960,"text":"This path you made for me,\nwhich bones had to break?"},{"time":145880,"text":"Did you do enough, and are you OK, momma?"},{"time":148160,"text":"And are you a hero?\""},{"time":149400,"text":"She will ask the difficult questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151840,"text":"She will not care\nabout the arc of your brow,"},{"time":154040,"text":"the weight of your clutch."},{"time":155320,"text":"She will not ask of your mentions."},{"time":157000,"text":"Your daughter, for whom you have\nalready carried so much, wants to know"},{"time":160400,"text":"what you brought, what gift,\nwhat light did you keep from extinction?"},{"time":163920,"text":"When they came for victims in the night,"},{"time":165880,"text":"did you sleep through it\nor were you roused?"},{"time":168000,"text":"What was the cost of staying woke?"},{"time":169680,"text":"What, in the year we said time's up,\nwhat did you do with your privilege?"},{"time":173170,"text":"Did you sup on others' squalor?"},{"time":174720,"text":"Did you look away\nor directly into the flame?"},{"time":176880,"text":"Did you know your skill\nor treat it like a liability?"},{"time":179440,"text":"Were you fooled by the epithets\nof \"nasty\" or \"less than\"?"},{"time":182800,"text":"Did you teach with an open heart\nor a clenched fist?"},{"time":185320,"text":"Where were you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":186560,"text":"Tell her the truth. Make it your life."},{"time":188440,"text":"Confirm it. Say, \"Daughter, I stood there"},{"time":190440,"text":"with the moment\ndrawn on my face like a dagger,"},{"time":192680,"text":"and flung it back at itself,"},{"time":194040,"text":"slicing space for you.\""},{"time":195480,"text":"Tell her the truth, how you lived\nin spite of crooked odds."},{"time":198320,"text":"Tell her you were brave,"},{"time":199600,"text":"and always, always\nin the company of courage,"},{"time":201960,"text":"mostly the days\nwhen you just had yourself."},{"time":204280,"text":"Tell her she was born as you were,"},{"time":206280,"text":"as your mothers before,\nand the sisters beside them,"},{"time":208920,"text":"in the age of legends, like always."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211040,"text":"Tell her she was born just in time,"},{"time":213760,"text":"just in time"},{"time":215520,"text":"to lead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216760,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}